author: AceShowbiz.com
title: Joe Jonas' DNCE Previews 'Cake by the Ocean' Music Video, Announces 'Swaay' EP
text:
Comments The full visuals, which will see some bikini-clad girls having a huge food fight on a beach, will premiere on October 16. 
An official music video for Joe Jonas ' new band DNCE's debut single "Cake by the Ocean" is underway. Before dropping it in its entirety on Friday, October 16, the group shared on Tuesday, October 13 a couple of previews via their social media pages. The first sneak-peek debuted on Instagram opens with a number of bikini-clad girls racing towards a giant piece of cake literally placed by the ocean. They then have a huge food fight while the crowd cheers them on and Jonas performs alongside his bandmates. A video posted by DNCE (@dnce) on Oct 13, 2015 at 6:21am PDT "FIRST LOOK FOR OUR "CAKE BY THE OCEAN" MUSIC VIDEO. A LIL MESSY," read a caption for the clip. DNCE treated fans to a longer preview of the music video through another teaser shared on YouTube. "Cake by the Ocean" is the first song to have surfaced from the four-piece's newly-announced EP "Swaay". The record is set to come out on October 23 via Republic Records.
